            <title type="html"><![CDATA[Tag]]></title>
            <link href="/atoms/tag/"/>
            <updated>2019-09-07T23:48:53+02:00</updated>
            <id>/atoms/tag/</id>
            <content type="html"><![CDATA[<div class="w-100 bg-grays-white flex flex-wrap">
    <div class="tag tag-secondary">tagged</div>
    <div class="tag tag-accent1">tagged</div>
    <div class="tag tag-accent2">tagged</div>
    <div class="tag tag-accent3">tagged</div>
</div>
<p>Hovers:</p>
<div class="w-100 bg-grays-white flex flex-wrap">
    <a href="#"><div class="tag tag-secondary">tagged</div></a>
    <a href="#"><div class="tag tag-accent1">tagged</div></a>
    <a href="#"><div class="tag tag-accent2">tagged</div></a>
    <a href="#"><div class="tag tag-accent3">tagged</div></a>
</div>

<p>Creates small styled tags.</p>
<p>All colors with a <em>light</em> or <em>light4</em> variant are used to generate tag styles.</p>
<p>Tags embedded in a link element get a hover color, which is the <em>base</em> or <em>light2</em> variant respectively.</p>
<p>Selectors added:</p>
<pre><code>.tag, .tag-[color]</code></pre>
<p>Behaviour added:</p>
<pre><code>a>.tag-[color]:hover, a.tag-[color]:hover</code></pre>
<p>Tag code:</p>
<iframe src="https://component.frisovandijk.com/source/atoms/_tag.scss" class="w-100 h5 br3 bg-grays-light4"></iframe>]]></content>
