            <link href="/atoms/wave/"/>
            <updated>2019-09-07T23:48:53+02:00</updated>
            <id>/atoms/wave/</id>
            <content type="html"><![CDATA[<div class="w-100 mv4 pb5 bg-grays-white">
    <div class="w-100 bg-primary pt4">
        <svg class="waves" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink" viewBox="0 24 150 28" preserveAspectRatio="none" shape-rendering="auto">
            <defs>
                <path id="waves--gentle" d="M-160 44c30 0 58-18 88-18s 58 18 88 18 58-18 88-18 58 18 88 18 v44h-352z" />
            </defs>
            <g class="waves__parallax">
                <use xlink:href="#waves--gentle" x="48" y="0" fill="rgba(190,208,0,0.7)" />
                <use xlink:href="#waves--gentle" x="48" y="3" fill="rgba(255,255,255,0.5)" />
                <use xlink:href="#waves--gentle" x="48" y="5" fill="rgba(255,255,255,0.3)" />
                <use xlink:href="#waves--gentle" x="48" y="7" fill="#fff" />
            </g>
        </svg>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="w-100 pa2 bg-grays-white flex flex-wrap">
    <div class="w-100 ph3 pv2">
        <p>Creates a responsive, pure CSS wave parrallax animation from 4 layered SVGs.</p>
        <p>Best used on full screen width.</p>
        <p>Example colors are set for a dark background flowing into white.</p>
        <p>Selectors added:</p>
        <pre class=""><code>.waves, .waves__parallax, #waves--gentle</code></pre>
        <p>Credit: <a href="https://codepen.io/csspoints/pen/WNeOEqd">CSS Points wave</a></p>
    </div>
<pre><code>&lt;svg class=&quot;waves&quot; xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&quot; xmlns:xlink=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink&quot; viewBox=&quot;0 24 150 28&quot; preserveAspectRatio=&quot;none&quot; shape-rendering=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;
    &lt;defs&gt;
    &lt;path id=&quot;waves--gentle&quot; d=&quot;M-160 44c30 0 58-18 88-18s 58 18 88 18 58-18 88-18 58 18 88 18 v44h-352z&quot; /&gt;
    &lt;/defs&gt;
    &lt;g class=&quot;waves__parallax&quot;&gt;
    &lt;use xlink:href=&quot;#waves--gentle&quot; x=&quot;48&quot; y=&quot;0&quot; fill=&quot;rgba(190,208,0,0.7)&quot; /&gt;
    &lt;use xlink:href=&quot;#waves--gentle&quot; x=&quot;48&quot; y=&quot;3&quot; fill=&quot;rgba(255,255,255,0.5)&quot; /&gt;
    &lt;use xlink:href=&quot;#waves--gentle&quot; x=&quot;48&quot; y=&quot;5&quot; fill=&quot;rgba(255,255,255,0.3)&quot; /&gt;
    &lt;use xlink:href=&quot;#waves--gentle&quot; x=&quot;48&quot; y=&quot;7&quot; fill=&quot;#fff&quot; /&gt;
    &lt;/g&gt;
    &lt;/svg&gt;
</code></pre>
    <p>Wave code:</p>
    <iframe src="https://component.frisovandijk.com/source/atoms/_wave.scss" class="w-100 h5 br3 bg-grays-light4"></iframe>
</div>]]></content>
